													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "After his initial shock reaction, Ketheric grabs the halberd with one hand and pulls it free. The wound left by the blade is just a glowing purple gash, which disappears before our eyes, leaving his chest without even a scratch."
