													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The terrified goblin picks up the halberd and swings to decapitate Ketheric, but it crashes into his neck, cracking bone. He doesn't flinch. Ketheric pulls out the halberd, which also leaves a glowing purple wound, and tosses it aside."
												}
